high_descs: move to the right a bit and face the bathroom sink again
grab the soap bar off of the right side of the bathroom sink
move to the left a bit and face the bathroom sink again
place the bar of soap inside the sink, rinse it off, then take it back out
move over to the cabinet to the left of the kitchen sink
place the bar of soap on top of the cabinet
anns.task_desc: place a rinsed off bar of soap on top of the cabinet

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the tub, then hang a left and walk up to the sink.
Pick up the bar of soap off of the counter to the right of the sink.
Turn left and walk towards the door, then turn around to face the sink.
Put the bar of soap in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean bar of soap.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right to face the cabinet.
Put the clean bar of soap on top of the cabinet to the right of the tissue box.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap on top of a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right and take a step, then turn left and walk to the sink.
Pick up the bar of soap on the counter.
Take a step left and walk to face the left side of the sink.
Wash the soap in the sink.
Turn around and walk in front of the shelves in front of you.
Place the soap on the dresser to the right of the tissue box.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed bar of soap on a shelving unit.
